## Quality Equation Components (Project 8)

**Formula:** Quality ≈ (Prompt Files × 0.65) + (Memory/Context × 0.20) + (Model × 0.10) + (Tools × 0.05)

**Current Assessment (estimated):**
- **Prompt Files:** 9.0/10 (complete agent files with Quality Equation integration)
